<HEADLINE>
<P>
BUCHANAN ON FUNDING FOR ART 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Buchanan's column was a breath of fresh air for the millions of us who are sick 
to death of funding the destruction of our cultural roots through our tax 
dollars. If we allow our Christian heritage and the morality it engenders to be 
destroyed by those with a pagan world view, we will see the United States 
destroyed. 
</P>
<P>
Defund, deflate and discipline the National Endowment for the Arts! 
</P>
<P>
VINCE ZEIMIS 
</P>
<P>
Redondo Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
