<SUBJECT>
<P>
SPORTS DEATHS; BOAT RACING; BOAT ACCIDENTS -- ARIZONA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA040390-0054 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 198752 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 3, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 5; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
