<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: POP/ROCK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BETH KLEID, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Crazy for You: Madonna fans snatched up the 60,000 tickets for the singer's 
four Los Angeles shows -- May 11, 12, 13 and 15 -- in 68 minutes. 
</P>
<P>
To meet the Madonna demand, a fifth date has been added for May 16. Tickets go 
on sale Wednesday at 8 a.m. at Music Plus outlets and through Ticketmaster's 
charge-by-phone number. Madonna fans across the country were equally voracious: 
All of the 500,000 tickets for the scheduled Madonna concerts nationwide were 
bought in just four hours. BETH KLEID 
</P>
