<P>
From Broadway to the 'City of Angels'?"City of Angels" may be on its way to the 
City of the Angels. The producers of the Larry Gelbart/Cy Coleman Broadway 
musical hope to begin previews Oct. 9 for a Century City production at the 
Shubert Theatre, said co-producer Roger Berlind. A spokesman for the Shubert 
Organization confirmed that "the intention is to have the show out here as soon 
as possible, but there is no booking at the moment." BETH KLEID 
</P>
