JEWS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- PALESTINIANS; PLO; HOLOCAUST; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT; MIDDLE EAST PEACE 
</P>
