<DOCID> 203524 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 3, 1990, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 9A; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
